abstract:

The used technologies are python based and include: MongoDB tensorflow Flask google.cloud python API A dataset of labelled satellite images is created. Several networks are trained and tested on this dataset. The network is deployed on a production server. The results of the classification/segmentaion are used to feed python based photovotlaic simulation libaries. The output is displayed and the results (the potential) evaluated.
---
full_description:

The used technologies are python based and include: MongoDB tensorflow Flask google.cloud python API

A dataset of labelled satellite images is created. Several networks are trained and tested on this dataset. The network is deployed on a production server.

The results of the classification/segmentaion are used to feed python based photovotlaic simulation libaries. The output is displayed and the results (the potential) evaluated.
